      <hedline>
        <hl1>QUOTATION OF THE DAY</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''If somebody wants to be entertained, they ought to go to the circus. They ought to go to the movies. Or they ought to go to the ballgame. I didn't sign on to entertain people for 90 minutes three times.''</p>
        <p>JIM LEHRER, on his role as moderator of the presidential debates. [A27]</p>
      </block>
